oot over bridge, and extensions buildings. It provides its services in Australia, Canada, Ireland, Latvia, Malaysia, New Zealand, Poland, Singapore, Sweden, the United Kingdom, and USA. Telge Projects Limited was incorporated in 2018 and is headquartered in Pune, India."}}